Comment: as a livelong Pats fan and as a transplanted Falcon fan for over years this was my dream Super Bowl The Falcons made the Pats look old and slow for almost quarters Some factors happened that were beyond the Falcons control but the simple fact is they choked The saddest part among many is the Julio miracle grab and the calls afterward The Falcons gave up a ton of draft capital for Julio to make that play at that moment And he did Matt Bryant had not missed inside yards the entire season You run the ball three times and if you must throw quick hitch screen with no deep drop It s like teams forget simple fundamentals when faced with the Pats And the coaching staff went braindead But all of that aside a simply amazing performance by the Pats Brady had to be perfect and from onward he was Edelman s catch was one in a million And what can you say about Hightower the big sack this Super Bowl and the full body sacrifice bringing down Lynch the play before Butler s miracle Amazing joy at the Pats win and crushing grief at another Falcon choke Did I say this was my dream Super Bowl

Comment: I am a huge Tom Brady fan and of my home team the NEP I can not say if Tom is the greatest player ever in the NFL but I can say that Tom his story the story of NEP is the wildest and most intriguing I have ever heard I have read and witnessed tons of amazing stories but this is just on another level It s so unscripted and yet inevitable It s why not me times a million The level of self belief and blinders on is just epic how can you not love this story even if you re rooting against him My son is on a CAA football team and I have seen through him and many of his teammates the story of just getting there as an epic act of overcoming and beating the odds and in our wildest dreams we could never expect the level of accomplishment and pure will to succeed as Tom has seen and experienced in his life Is he the greatest football player to ever take the field Couldn t tell you his s sure dictate as much Is he the greatest example of over coming one s own physical being to achieve what no other person ever has Absolutely Through his example of self belief he is the most amazing person in the game right now and the greatest inspiration one could have to push themselves to their goals
